OL,3,CFirst-ever monument in the UK to
OL,4,Chonour Roma Holocaust victims unveiled
OL,6,FA monument has been erected in
OL,7,FNewcastle dedicated to remembering the
OL,8,Fsuffering and murder of the Roma
OL,9,Fduring the Holocaust.
OL,11,FIt is the first, and only permanent,
OL,12,Fmemorial in the UK for the victims of
OL,13,Fthe genocide of the Roma.
OL,15,FThe exact number of Romani people who
OL,16,Fdied during World War II at the hands
OL,17,Fof the Nazi regime is unknown - but it
OL,18,Fis thought it could be as many as half
OL,19,Fa million people.
