OL,3,CFirst-ever monument in the UK to
OL,4,Chonour Roma Holocaust victims unveiled
OL,6,FThe memorial unveiled on 1 August
OL,7,Fhopes to serve as a tranquil space for
OL,8,Fvisiting families and friends, as a
OL,9,Fplace of reflection and to ensure
OL,10,Fthose who lost their lives will not be
OL,11,Fforgotten.
OL,13,FITV Tyne Tees spoke to one woman at
OL,14,Fthe event, who shared how "important"
OL,15,Fthe commemoration was for her family.
