OL,3,CFirst-ever monument in the UK to
OL,4,Chonour Roma Holocaust victims unveiled
OL,6,FShe said: "It's very important to me,
OL,7,Fespecially my family, because my
OL,8,Fgrandfather's father died in
OL,9,FAuschwitz, but unfortunately we have
OL,10,Fno memory of that, because of World
OL,11,FWar II.
OL,13,F"It means a lot to us to have the
OL,14,Fmemorial stone here today."
OL,16,FAnother person said that it was
OL,17,F"really amazing" that this happened,
OL,18,Fwhilst another said "I'm really happy
OL,19,Fto see what Newcastle Council has done
OL,20,Ffor the Roma community."
