OL,3,CFirst-ever monument in the UK to
OL,4,Chonour Roma Holocaust victims unveiled
OL,6,FIn 2023, former Councillor Nicu Ion
OL,7,Fintroduced a motion to Newcastle City
OL,8,FCouncil, leading to the official
OL,9,Frecognition of the day - 2 August -
OL,10,Fbeing a day of commemoration for the
OL,11,FRoma victims of the Holocaust.
OL,13,FAs part of this initiative, the
OL,14,Fcouncil pledged to provide a space at
OL,15,Fthe Civic Centre for a dedicated
OL,16,Fmemorial.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
