OL,3,CFirst-ever monument in the UK to
OL,4,Chonour Roma Holocaust victims unveiled
OL,6,FNicu Ion attended the unveiling event
OL,7,Fand spoke about how the memorial is
OL,8,Falso dedicated to soldiers from the
OL,9,FNorth East, who helped free the Roma
OL,10,Fsurvivors of the Holocaust.
OL,12,F"It's really important to acknowledge
OL,13,Fthe British soldiers from the North
OL,14,FEast who actually fight to liberate
OL,15,Fthe concentration camps, where Roma
OL,16,Fwere prisoners, and Bergen Belsen is
OL,17,Fone of them, where the majority of
OL,18,Fprisoners in those camps were actually
OL,19,FRoma.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
