OL,4,Chonour Roma Holocaust victims unveiled
OL,6,F"So we wanted to pay a special tribute
OL,7,Fto the British soldiers, so there's a
OL,8,Fpowerful connection," he said.
OL,10,FIt is hoped that the memorial can be
OL,11,Fused to educate others about the Roma
OL,12,Fvictims of the Holocaust.
OL,14,FRuth-Anne Lenga, from the
OL,15,FInternational Holocaust Remembrance
OL,16,FAlliance (IHRA), said: "It's been so
OL,17,Flong forgotten. It's been ignored.
OL,18,FThere's not enough research about it,
OL,19,Fand teachers really struggle to know
OL,20,Fenough to feel confident to teach
OL,21,Fabout this subject.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
